answers.text: . One of them, led by general Platen in September resulted in the loss of 2,000 Russians, mostly captured, and the destruction of 5,000 wagons

qas.question: Identify a major Prussian loss to the Russians

answers.text: Russians under Zakhar Chernyshev and Pyotr Rumyantsev stormed Kolberg in Pomerania

answers.text: . In Britain, it was speculated that a total Prussian collapse was now imminent.
